f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5468cdc8a2eb4eed599a7dd02d859fc79a780f","tid":472004,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T19:36:31.000Z","msg":"照copy係可以，但要加番&quot;&quot; 同括番邊度黎<br />\n然後再解釋，點去support你既觀點而唔係成為你既觀點"},{"pid":"31cbf5388bbbd960b7ee285bb2e5228c83ee53b1","tid":472004,"uid":45773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T19:41:11.000Z","msg":"屌，連direct quotation都唔識用，你讀邊間大學呀，痕大定中大(深圳)？"},{"pid":"fdd4502666ec7f436506e34965447aaae7aebc40","tid":472004,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:13:13.000Z","msg":"就算用左直接引用做好哂註解<br />\n如果呢段野就係你篇文既最重要部分都係唔會高分"},{"pid":"196d673b41d675ebe6240c84df279f2211cbcbc9","tid":472004,"uid":144198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T03:28:06.000Z","msg":"paraphrase有咁難咩"},{"pid":"a4c92b2f9ddfd7943fad9becc6099d0dd1bcd963","tid":472004,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T03:35:30.000Z","msg":"間間大學唔一樣，你自己問番老師先啦"},{"pid":"d3ca7765ca47a80d9cb4bd54b1cf4010a2828ebf","tid":472004,"uid":11977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T03:40:30.000Z","msg":"direct quotation 唔可以超過全文10% 好似係"}]}